{
  "stem": "4967.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] But he didn't know-- he didn't know, this policeman, that his family is hiding in this particular hideout.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he told the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he showed the Germans where the hideout is.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Germans took out all the people in the hideout, and they shot them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was standing the Jewish policeman, who saw that his wife and one of his children got shot as well.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in several cases like this was in the ghetto, the people were afraid to talk to each other about hideouts or about other things in case somebody would go and get a reward or get a special certificate, which will prolong his life for another day, another hour.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Excuse me.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [DRINKS] And life got on in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "People died every day.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "One afternoon, Sunday afternoon, the German trucks were driving around the ghetto, with [INAUDIBLE], or loudspeakers, as you say now, that everybody must come to a certain assembly place.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We thought already they are going to make another selection.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A selection means that they're going to select the people who are to survive in the ghetto or to be sent out from the ghetto to be liquidated.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we come to this big place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And here they are still erecting a big pole and a platform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they're making-- they're building a hanging place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "How do you call it in English?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "A gallows.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And here they bring the poor Jewish guy, handcuffed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they put him on the platform.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody had to watch.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Then they put the rope on his neck, and they pulled the blocks or whatever it was under his legs, and he was hanged.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
